OL,3,CFour people in hospital after being
OL,4,Cexposed to chemicals in spa
OL,6,FEmergency services outside the
OL,7,FClifford Health Club and Spa in Long
OL,8,FEaton
OL,10,FFour people have been taken to
OL,11,Fhospital after being exposed to
OL,12,F"excess chlorine" in a Derbyshire spa.
OL,14,FDerbyshire Fire Service and East
OL,15,FMidlands Ambulance were called to a
OL,16,Freported a medical emergency on Regent
OL,17,FStreet, Long Eaton at around 10:30
OL,18,Fthis morning.
