OL,3,CFour people in hospital after being
OL,4,Cexposed to chemicals in spa
OL,6,F27 people were exposed to excess
OL,7,Fchlorine in the spa area of the
OL,8,Fbuilding. Ten of the 27 people were
OL,9,Fshowing symptoms relating to the
OL,10,Fexposure and were treated at the scene
OL,11,Fby paramedics. Four people have been
OL,12,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,14,FThe fire service said none of the
OL,15,Fsymptoms suffered were serious and
OL,16,Fthat the Health and Safety Executive
OL,17,Fhad been informed.
