OL,3,CFour people in hospital after being
OL,4,Cexposed to chemicals in spa
OL,6,FA staff member at spa in Long Eaton
OL,7,Ftold ITV Central: "We heard people had
OL,8,Fpassed out in the spa and management
OL,9,Ftold us to leave the building."
OL,11,F"All clients have been sent home and
OL,12,Fstaff have been able to go back into
OL,13,Fthe building.
OL,15,F"The gym and the offices are open but
OL,16,Fthe ground floor is still closed."
