OL,3,CFour people in hospital after being
OL,4,Cexposed to chemicals in spa
OL,6,FThe East Midlands Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fsaid: "We sent a number of resources
OL,8,Fincluding two paramedics in two
OL,9,Fambulance cars, two crewed ambulances,
OL,10,Four Hazardous Area Response Team and a
OL,11,Fresponder from the air ambulance."
OL,13,FIn a message sent from the spa to its
OL,14,Fmembers, seen by ITV News Central, The
OL,15,FClifford Health Club said: "Following
OL,16,Fan incident this morning during normal
OL,17,Fpool maintenance, the relevant
OL,18,Fauthorities have now given us the ok
OL,19,Fto safely open the pool and spa from
OL,20,F2pm."
